    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this absolute stunner in person. Honestly, it\u2019s like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014the paint is flawless and it still has that amazing new-car smell! I\u2019ve totally babied this beauty since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and detailed regularly. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s in truly pristine, showroom condition, this is definitely the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin, I promise you\u2019ll fall in love!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
